Sta-lube makes the stuff.  Usually available at most FLAPS.  You can also
use Redline MT-90, which is synthetic, safe for your transmission, and
kind of expensive.  Since I don't change tranny lube all that often, the
extra expense isn't important to me.

George Lyle

